# Changelog

## [2.0.0] - 2024-12-27

Removal of Variables Template dependency.

- Removed parameter for VariablesTemplateRelativePath (@srjames-ukho)
- Added parameter for JobsVariablesMappings (@srjames-ukho)
- Added expression for iterating over new parameter to add variables to jobs (@srjames-ukho)
- Added relevant documentation regarding new JobsVariableMappings feature and upgrading through major breaking change (@srjames-ukho)
- Refactored documentation for ease of future updates (@srjames-ukho)
- Added yaml pipeline file for testing the usage of the template (@sentonnes)

## [1.0.0] - 2024-07-26

Initial release of migrated template.

- Migrated and updated template for new repository (@srjames-ukho)
- Migrated and updated docs for new repository (@srjames-ukho)